episodes.overview: DiNozzo is reunited with his ex-girlfriend, Jeanne Benoit, when insurgents in Sudan attack a group of volunteer doctors, including her husband.  DiNozzo and McGee travel to the crime scene for the joint murder and kidnapping case and join the search for the missing doctors.

episodes.name: Day in Court
episodes.overview: In order to clear his name, a petty officer volunteers to be court martialed if NCIS agrees to conduct its own investigation after his murder case is dismissed due to a mishandled warrant. Also, Bishop and Jake discuss their marital problems.

episodes.name: Blood Brothers
episodes.overview: The Secretary of Defense calls on NCIS to help a sailor who is battling leukemia to locate a donor for a bone marrow transplant, after two of his siblings are killed in the line of duty.  Meanwhile, Bishop returns home to Oklahoma for Thanksgiving.

episodes.name: Spinning Wheel
episodes.overview: After Ducky is attacked by a man claiming to have information about his half-brother who died decades ago, the NCIS team searches for the perpetrator, as Ducky recalls the final emotional days he had with his sibling.  Also, with the holidays approaching, Bishop and Jake discuss the future of their relationship.

episodes.name: Sister City (I)
episodes.overview:
The passengers and crew of a private plane traveling from New Orleans to Washington, D.C., are poisoned and the evidence points to Abby's brother, the aircraft's missing chef.

The episode continues on NCIS: New Orleans S2E12 Sister City (II).

guest_stars.character: Navy Petty Officer First Class Felix Kane
guest_stars.name: Abraham Amkpa

episodes.name: Déjà Vu
episodes.overview: While investigating the murder of a seaman who was set to testify before a grand jury, the NCIS team uncovers the resurgence of an international human-trafficking ring.  Also, McGee hopes to spend the night at a colleague’s home after a storm causes massive power outages in the city.

episodes.name: Decompressed
episodes.overview: Four deep sea divers stay inside a diving chamber with a deceased body in order to decompress. The dead body belongs to a retired petty officer who died in mysterious circumstances. The NCIS team will try to crack the case from land while the divers spend four days with the body.

episodes.name: React
episodes.overview: When Secretary of the Navy Sarah Porter learns her daughter has been kidnapped, the NCIS team partners with the FBI to track the case, determine a motive and bring her home. Also, McGee’s childhood friend, NCIS Special Agent Valerie Page is in town to assist the team with advance tactics training

episodes.name: Loose Cannons
episodes.overview: Doctor Cyril Taft experiences the rush of an NCIS case after he is assigned surgical duty to Gibb’s suspect and finds key evidence. Also, Dinozzo pays Jeanne Benoit a visit as he chases a lead involving doctors in Sudan.

episodes.name: After Hours
episodes.overview: The NCIS agents’ personal plans are interrupted when each of them catches errors in a seemingly cut-and-dried closed case. Also, McGee and Delilah argue over the importance of not discussing work during dinner, while DiNozzo bores his date with shop talk.

episodes.name: Scope
episodes.overview: The NCIS team re-examines an ambush on a group of Special Ops snipers in Iraq after an American couple is attacked in the same area six months later. When Gibbs discovers he needs the account of the lone survivor, Marine Gunnery Sergeant Aaron Davis, he tries to connect with the wounded warrior who is being treated for PTSD at Walter Reed Medical Center.

episodes.name: Reasonable Doubts
episodes.overview: A Navy Public Affairs officer is murdered, and the victim's wife and mistress accuse each other of the crime. Meanwhile, Anthony DiNozzo Sr. helps a homeless woman who believes he is her father.

episodes.name: Charade
episodes.overview: Tony's identity is stolen by multiple perpetrators who go on to blackmail politicians.

episodes.name: Return to Sender
episodes.overview: Gibbs and Senior FBI Agent T.C. Fornell unite after two British prisoners, including a former spy, escape and arrive stateside via a shipping container. Also, McGee is busy apartment hunting and determined to find out how DiNozzo purchased his lavish place.

episodes.name: Homefront
episodes.overview: When a 14-year-old foils a home invasion, Gibbs suspects the teenager is withholding pertinent details. Also, Director Vance and Senior FBI Agent Fornell travel to London as part of the ongoing escaped British spy case.

guest_stars.character: Harper's Ferry Police Officer Kristin Fields
guest_stars.name: Zoe Perry

episodes.name: Dead Letter
episodes.overview: The NCIS team, alongside the FBI and MI6, continue an international manhunt for an escaped British spy who has left one colleague fighting for their life in ICU.

episodes.name: Family First
episodes.overview: NCIS, FBI and MI6 continue an international manhunt for an escaped British spy who is targeting current and former agents.

episodes.name: Rogue
episodes.overview: The NCIS team investigates a deadly car explosion in D.C. that connects to NCIS Special Agent Nicholas “Nick” Torres, who disappeared six months ago while on a deep undercover assignment in Argentina. Also, Gibbs asks NCIS Special Agent Alexandra “Alex” Quinn to shadow his team after rejecting eight agents she instructed and referred for the open position.

episodes.name: Being Bad
episodes.overview: NCIS uncovers a bomb plot and a long-running theft ring while investigating a death at a Quantico reunion. Also Torres and Quinn adjust to life on Gibbs’ team, including new seating arrangements in the squad room.

episodes.name: Privileged Information
episodes.overview: When the NCIS team investigates a marine sergeant’s tragic fall from a building, her doctor, Grace Confalone, confides in Gibbs and suggests he treat it as a murder investigation. Also, Torres searches for a place to live.

episodes.name: Love Boat
episodes.overview: After the body of a navy lieutenant is discovered aboard a destroyer during a tiger cruise, when civilian guests are allowed to spend the night on the ship, Gibbs, Quinn and Palmer travel out to sea to investigate. Also, McGee contemplates the perfect proposal for Delilah Fielding.

guest_stars.character: Navy Petty Officer 1st Class Tyrell Brown
guest_stars.name: Mike Wade

episodes.name: Philly
episodes.overview: When a missing MI6 Officer is linked to a murdered petty officer, Gibbs sends Quinn and Bishop to Philadelphia to work with MI6 Officer Clayton Reeves. Also, Quinn painfully recounts the NCIS case that made her leave field work.

episodes.name: Shell Game
episodes.overview: After a kidnapped petty officer escapes her captor, NCIS uncovers a connection to her missing husband. Also, Abby knits the NCIS newbies personalized gifts.

episodes.name: Home of the Brave
episodes.overview: Torres boldly breaks protocol when he learns a witness in an NCIS case is wanted by U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement. Also, Abby, Bishop and McGee woo landlord Tony DiNozzo Sr. in the hope of subletting Tony’s apartment.

episodes.name: Enemy Combatant
episodes.overview: After NCIS Agent Bishop is sent to Gitmo to gather evidence for a Navy chaplain murder case, she questions her previous work at the NSA. Also, Bishop’s brothers, John and Robert, visit for the Thanksgiving holiday and pester her co-workers to find out who she is dating.

episodes.name: Pay to Play
episodes.overview: The NCIS team investigates a series of escalating threats against congresswoman Jenna Flemming,  while Director Vance oversees her temporary protection detail.

episodes.name: The Tie That Binds
episodes.overview: After the NCIS team tracks evidence from the murder of a Navy captain to Ducky’s deceased mother, Ducky looks back and questions a pivotal life choice he made 37 years ago. Also, the team exchanges holiday gifts, and Gibbs spends Christmas dinner with Fornell.

episodes.name: Willoughby
episodes.overview: NCIS searches for new leads after an undercover operation to apprehend a businessman who uses acts of terror to manipulate the stock market is compromised. Also, Bishop and Qasim find a break in the case together.

episodes.name: Off the Grid
episodes.overview: When Gibbs spots the brother of an "NCIS Most Wanted" suspect, he takes the opportunity to assume his former alias and go undercover with their infamous anti-government militia. This leaves the NCIS team to piece together where and what Gibbs is up to. Meanwhile, Bishop and Reeves partner up on an off-the-books investigation.

episodes.name: Keep Going
episodes.overview: During an NCIS hit-and-run investigation, Palmer joins a stranger on the outside ledge of a building in an attempt to save his life.

episodes.name: Nonstop
episodes.overview: The murder of a Petty Officer in a small town outside D.C. prompts NCIS to once again work with "The Sherlocks," a privately funded investigative team that includes their newest member, Anthony DiNozzo, Sr.

episodes.name: Pandora's Box (I)
episodes.overview:
After Abby's homeland security think tank is compromised and she is found in possession of a real bomb, the NCIS team discovers the leader of the group has been murdered and a theoretical terror playbook has been stolen.

The crossover continues on NCIS: New Orleans S03E14 Pandora's Box (II).

episodes.name: A Many Splendored Thing
episodes.overview: Bishop is more determined than ever to seek revenge for the murder of Qasim, her late boyfriend, after Gibbs and the team find a new lead in the Chen case. Also, Torres teaches the agents the art of pickpocketing.

episodes.name: What Lies Above
episodes.overview: McGee discovers his apartment has been torn apart by a robber trying to locate an item of great value hidden somewhere by the convicted criminal who previously owned the unit. Also, Congresswoman Flemming (Mary Stuart Masterson) tries to persuade Director Vance to pursue a career in politics.

episodes.name: M.I.A.
episodes.overview: To carry out a sailor's dying wish, Gibbs and the NCIS team reinvestigate a murder case that was originally ruled an accidental death. Also, the case reminds Torres of a tragic time from his past.

episodes.name: The Wall
episodes.overview: The team must rely on an irritable Vietnam War veteran to solve a Marine's murder.

episodes.name: A Bowl of Cherries
episodes.overview: A vice admiral tasks McGee with tracking down the hackers who infected his laptop with ransomware before the virus wipes out all his data. The cyberterrorism escalates when the virus spreads to the whole NCIS office. Quinn's family secret is revealed.

episodes.name: One Book, Two Covers
episodes.overview: A Marine's murder has connections to a dirt bike gang that Torres joined while on an old undercover operation.

episodes.name: Beastmaster
episodes.overview: A gunnery sergeant's murder in a national park lead the team to join forces with the mounted police. While investigating the clues, they uncover a disturbing smuggling ring.

episodes.name: Something Blue
episodes.overview: The team suspects foul play when a healthy, young petty officer mysteriously dies in his sleep aboard a Navy destroyer. Wedding stress reaches its peak for McGee and his fiancée.

episodes.name: Rendezvous
episodes.overview: When a Navy SEAL vanishes during  an unsanctioned trip, Gibbs, McGee and Torres travel to an unpopulated area in Paraguay that's teeming with violent rebels.

episodes.name: House Divided
episodes.overview: Season 15 begins with the NCIS team tirelessly searching for Gibbs and McGee two months after they were last seen fighting an elusive group of rebels in a Paraguay jungle. Meanwhile, Vance and Torres are summoned to a congressional hearing regarding the fallout from the Paraguay mission.

episodes.name: Twofer
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates when the body of a murdered Navy lieutenant, who disappeared over a year ago, is found by a cemetery grounds crew while relocating caskets on the property. Meanwhile, Gibbs and McGee must pass a psych evaluation before they can officially resume working.

episodes.name: Exit Strategy
episodes.overview: Torres' partner mysteriously vanishes during a stakeout with Metro P.D. The investigation uncovers new evidence from a decade-old murder case. Meanwhile, Ducky's friend, Cadence Darwin, presents him with a new opportunity during his guest lecture series.

episodes.name: Skeleton Crew
episodes.overview: NCIS Special Agent Jacqueline Sloane, a forensic psychologist, joins the team just as a horrific storm shuts down Washington, D.C. During the power outage, a sailor is kidnapped, and Torres and Bishop go out to sea to track evidence.

episodes.name: Fake It ‘Till You Make It
episodes.overview: Reeves sees his friend get kidnapped and the investigation reveals the primary suspect disappeared two days earlier with confidential military information. Meanwhile, an embarrassing photo from McGee’s teen years becomes a popular meme.

episodes.name: Trapped
episodes.overview: A petty officer is found murdered on a golf course, and McGee spends hours on the victim’s ham radio trying to locate a key witness. Meanwhile, Palmer asks his co-workers to donate to a charity that builds playgrounds for kids of all abilities, and Torres surprises them with his generosity.

episodes.name: Burden of Proof
episodes.overview: A convicted felon claims NCIS framed him for murder a decade ago, so Gibbs investigates and asks Ducky to conduct a new autopsy. Meanwhile, Senior FBI agent Fornell joins the probe, since he was the lead investigator in the original joint FBI and NCIS case.

episodes.name: Voices
episodes.overview: An NCIS person of interest in a bribery and fraud case is found murdered after a runner is led to his body by a strange voice. Also, McGee and Delilah disagree on whether to find out the baby’s sex or keep it a surprise.

episodes.name: Ready or Not
episodes.overview: The team tracks an elusive international arms dealer who recently murdered an MI6 officer; Abby races Delilah to the hospital when her labor starts three weeks early.

episodes.name: Double Down
episodes.overview: As Torres and Sloane run protection detail for U.S. Senator John Phillips in Afghanistan for the holidays, they must urgently return to the states after hearing the senator’s son is in the ICU. Also, Gibbs and the team investigate the altercation that caused the life threatening injuries to the senator’s son.

episodes.name: High Tide
episodes.overview: Torres and Bishop go undercover as a criminal couple available for hire, during an NCIS sting operation tracking illegal drug-running out of the Norfolk civilian marina.

episodes.name: Dark Secrets
episodes.overview: After a seemingly happy and successful Navy lieutenant appears to have taken her own life, Gibbs and the team conduct a thorough investigation, interviewing family and friends from her past and present.

episodes.name: Family Ties
episodes.overview: After McGee and Torres visit the home of a high schooler who witnessed a hit-and-run, her parents, Christopher and Julie Bell, flee with their daughter, leaving NCIS in the lurch. Also, Vance’s daughter is arrested for shoplifting.

episodes.name: Keep Your Friends Close
episodes.overview: After the body of a missing Navy commander is found, Vance orders Gibbs and the team to work with former FBI Agent Tobias "T.C." Fornell, the private investigator who was hired to locate him. Also, Bishop and Torres interview convicted investment advisor Albert Hathaway when the victim is linked to his highly publicized trial.

episodes.name: Keep Your Enemies Closer
episodes.overview: NCIS strikes a deal with convicted murderer Paul Triff, giving him a 48-hour furlough at his former residence, now McGee's home, in exchange for information that can convict his former cellmate, Gabriel Hicks, the murderer who deceived Gibbs and Fornell.

episodes.name: Handle with Care
episodes.overview: Gibbs and the team work to clear the name of retired Marine Sergeant John Ross when cyanide is found in one of the hundreds of care packages he sends to active-duty Marines.

guest_stars.character: Navy Petty Officer Third Class Gordon Cooper
guest_stars.name: Tyler Parks

guest_stars.character: Navy Petty Officer Second Class James Sweeney
guest_stars.name: Jake Allyn

episodes.name: One Man's Trash
episodes.overview: Gibbs and Ducky are watching TV when they see the host handling a 200-year-old war stick that could be a match from a decade-old cold case.

episodes.name: Death from Above
episodes.overview: The NCIS headquarters are evacuated after the team discovers a body as well as bomb materials on the roof of the squad room. Also, the team reads the first draft of Ducky’s book.

episodes.name: The Numerical Limit
episodes.overview: Gibbs is granted protective custody of a 10-year-old orphaned refugee, Elena, when an NCIS case reveals she is the target of a violent gang.

episodes.name: Sight Unseen
episodes.overview: NCIS searches for a petty officer suspected of assault who escapes when the sheriff transporting him crashes into a lake. Also, Torres works closely with Annie Barth, a key blind witness who heard vital evidence needed to solve the case.

episodes.name: One Step Forward
episodes.overview: Sara Carter begs Gibbs to investigate her mother's murder; she believes the wrong man was convicted; Abby is awarded a dinner reservation for two to a new five-star restaurant in an igloo and has to decide which co-worker deserves to go with her.

episodes.name: Two Steps Back
episodes.overview: When evidence reveals an NCIS team member is a hitman’s latest target, the team must search through old case files to determine who is seeking vengeance.

episodes.name: Fallout
episodes.overview: While Gibbs attends the memorial service for a friend who was lost at sea, he discovers that the deceased, Navy Captain Phillip Brooks, has been hiding in a fallout shelter after his boat was attacked and he swam to shore.

episodes.name: Date with Destiny
episodes.overview: Sloane is adamant that a man who held her hostage and tortured her years ago in Afghanistan, and was believed to have been killed following her rescue, is alive and in D.C. Also, Vance and Gibbs fear Sloane is willing to risk everything to destroy this man.

episodes.name: Destiny's Child
episodes.overview: One month after Director Vance was kidnapped, Gibbs is assigned the role of acting director in his absence while the team searches worldwide for his whereabouts.

episodes.name: Love Thy Neighbor
episodes.overview: After a Navy lieutenant is found murdered in his hot tub, the team interviews several families in the victim’s peculiar neighborhood. Also, Torres must face the consequences after a volatile night out with Palmer.

episodes.name: Boom
episodes.overview: One of the NCIS agents is starstruck after the team investigates an explosion outside the home of Navy Petty Officer First Class Todd Nicholas and his wife, popular reality TV star Sheba Nicholas. Also, Vance continues physical therapy for the injuries sustained when he was held hostage.

episodes.name: Third Wheel
episodes.overview: Gibbs’ quiet vacation at his remote cabin is interrupted by a surprise visit from Tobias Fornell and Navy Captain Phillip Brooks, as well as a call from NCIS asking for his help locating a robber hiding in the woods near him.

episodes.name: Fragments
episodes.overview: After a 50-year-old tape recording left by a murder victim is found, the NCIS team tries to exonerate Ray Jennings, the Marine serving a life sentence for the crime.

guest_stars.character: Young Marine Lance Corporal Ray Jennings
guest_stars.name: Demetrius Hodges

episodes.name: Beneath the Surface
episodes.overview: After NCIS arrives at a Halloween crime scene, Torres recognizes the victim as a friend from federal law enforcement training. Also, Jimmy thinks his lab is haunted by ghosts after objects keep mysteriously moving.

episodes.name: A Thousand Words
episodes.overview: After a mural by a street artist and activist is stolen, the NCIS investigation leads to a conspiracy regarding a Navy contractor and the safety of ocean mammals. Also, Bishop shares a special connection with the street artist.

episodes.name: Friendly Fire
episodes.overview: McGee and Bishop travel to Afghanistan after a murder case in the states is linked to a string of soldiers killed by friendly fire overseas. Also, Kasie leaves the lab and accompanies Torres into the field to process additional forensic evidence.

episodes.name: Tailing Angie
episodes.overview: When the lead suspect of an unsolved and high-profile robbery case is released from prison, the NCIS team resumes their investigation with an undercover stakeout.

episodes.name: What Child is This?
episodes.overview: The team’s holiday plans are put on hold when the murder investigation of a Navy veteran includes the discovery of a newborn baby who has no identification and no apparent ties to a family.

episodes.name: Toil and Trouble
episodes.overview: United States Secretary of Defense Wynn Crawford shuts down Gibbs' murder investigation and demands that Special Agents McGee and Torres be arrested for their actions in the case.

episodes.name: The Last Link
episodes.overview: An old family friend, Army Corporal John Sydney, beseeches Gibbs to join him on a road trip to search for a missing military I.D. bracelet. Also, a Navy Lieutenant in NCIS protective custody is poisoned by an infamous drug dealer.

episodes.name: She
episodes.overview: After a malnourished and confused 9-year-old is found hiding in a storage unit, NCIS reopens an old missing persons case when the girl is believed to be the daughter of a Navy recruit who disappeared 10 years ago. Also, Bishop discovers notes that Special Agent Ziva David kept on the case long after NCIS officially stopped investigating.

episodes.name: Once Upon a Tim
episodes.overview: McGee reluctantly visits his high school after the unique computer password he used as a teenager is linked to the murder of a department of defense contractor. The case escalates when an intruder breaks into McGee’s home in an attempt to steal his archaic high school computer.

episodes.name: Crossing the Line
episodes.overview: The NCIS team investigates a man overboard fatality from a Navy destroyer at sea. Also, Torres is frustrated with Vance’s assignment to mentor three high school students.

episodes.name: Bears and Cubs
episodes.overview: Jimmy is torn between family and work after his father-in-law, Ed, asks him to tamper with evidence from NCIS’ current murder investigation. Also, Ed’s poker buddy, Anthony DiNozzo, Sr., offers to help with the case.

episodes.name: Silent Service
episodes.overview: Director Vance is notified by the Pentagon that the nuclear submarine Gibbs and Bishop are aboard to conduct a murder investigation has gone radio silent.

episodes.name: Mona Lisa
episodes.overview: Torres relies on his team's investigative skills after he wakes up on a dilapidated fishing boat and is covered in blood and unable to remember the last 12 hours.

episodes.name: Perennial
episodes.overview: Following an active shooter lockdown at a naval hospital, the team searches for a suspect who fled the scene; someone from Sloane's past is a key witness in the case.

episodes.name: Hail & Farewell
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates the murder of a Marine Major believed to have been killed in the 9/11 attack on the Pentagon after human remains are discovered at a construction site. A personal history with the victim drives Gibbs to solve her crime.

episodes.name: Judge, Jury...
episodes.overview: After entering cold case DNA into the system, Kasie solves a 30-year-old murder case, but a loophole in the legal system may set the suspect free. Also, McGee visits an elite technology company in Silicon Valley that is offering him a highly paid position.

guest_stars.character: Navy Petty Officer First Class Kyle Larson (Age30s)
guest_stars.name: Austin Iredale

episodes.name: ...and Executioner
episodes.overview: After NCIS finds a secret government bank account that’s funding a nationwide network of vigilante justice, the team must determine who is acting as judge and jury.

episodes.name: Lost Time
episodes.overview: The NCIS team investigates the murder of a Marine Sergeant in the States who was hailed as a war hero for his efforts overseas. Also, Gibbs turns to Doctor Grace Confalone for advice after he uncharacteristically unravels and abandons his team at a crime scene investigation.

episodes.name: Daughters
episodes.overview: Former FBI Agent Tobias Fornell pleads with Gibbs to do whatever is necessary to take down drug dealers and suppliers in the area after his daughter, Emily Fornell, is hospitalized from an opiate overdose. Gibbs is haunted by the personal aspects of the case and his history with vigilante justice.

episodes.name: Out of the Darkness
episodes.overview: Ziva surprises Gibbs with a cryptic warning, prompting him to question why she remained underground for years while being presumed dead by family and friends, and what led to her return.

episodes.name: Into the Light
episodes.overview: With their lives in danger, Gibbs and Ziva’s rogue investigation takes an unexpected turn when a possible terrorist plot is revealed.

episodes.name: Going Mobile
episodes.overview: After the body of a Marine Lieutenant is found hidden under an 18-wheeler, the NCIS team tracks the vehicle’s previous locations to pinpoint the crime scene and suspect. Also, Sloane encourages the team to sit down and talk about Ziva’s recent reappearance.

guest_stars.character: Zullow Senior Vice President Lance Rama
guest_stars.name: David L. King

episodes.name: Someone Else's Shoes
episodes.overview: The NCIS team links a bizarre crime scene at Arlington National Cemetery to a string of attacks on homeless veterans. Also, Vance orders McGee, Bishop and Torres to complete hours of evidence garage cleanup duty for withholding information.

episodes.name: Wide Awake
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates Marine Corporal Laney Alimonte after evidence suggests she murdered her neighbor while being treated for insomnia by a hypnotherapist. Also, Gibbs befriends his new neighbors after the 9-year-old’s baseball crashes through his window.

episodes.name: Institutionalized
episodes.overview: After a petty officer’s son is found murdered at his “welcome home from prison” party, evidence suggests Kasie’s lifelong best friend, Dante Brown, is the suspect.

guest_stars.character: Master Chief Petty Officer Renee Quichera
guest_stars.name: Bertila Damas

episodes.name: No Vacancy
episodes.overview: While investigating a Marine’s murder, the NCIS team uncovers a labyrinth of live-streaming spy cameras hidden in the rooms of a Virginia motel.

guest_stars.character: U.S. Congressman for Virginia Eric Riley
guest_stars.name: Aaron Craven

episodes.name: Musical Chairs
episodes.overview: The NCIS team investigates the murder of a musician in the Navy’s most elite band that performs at diplomatic events around the world.

episodes.name: IRL
episodes.overview: The NCIS team investigates a petty officer's murder that was livestreamed on a popular gaming app; Gibbs watches his 11-year-old neighbor when his mom must leave on a last-minute trip.

episodes.name: The North Pole
episodes.overview: Gibbs and the team help Ziva with the "one thing" she said she'd take care of before returning to her family.

episodes.name: In the Wind
episodes.overview: Gibbs must face the consequences of helping Ziva with "the one thing" she said she'd take care of before returning to her family.

episodes.name: Flight Plan
episodes.overview: The NCIS team investigates an F-18 crash and the subsequent disappearance of the pilot; McGee reluctantly discusses a very personal decision with his teammates.

episodes.name: Sound Off
episodes.overview: After a body is found at an unmanned aerial vehicle testing site, the NCIS team must determine if the death was murder or an accident. Also, Palmer carefully interviews medical examiner assistant candidates

episodes.name: On Fire
episodes.overview: After Torres and Bishop are victims of a hit-and-run, Torres fights for his life in the Intensive Care Unit.

episodes.name: Lonely Hearts
episodes.overview: The lead suspect in an NCIS murder investigation is a woman Gibbs' friend, Phillip Brooks, met on a dating site. Also, Sloane has a secret admirer on Valentine's Day.

episodes.name: Ephemera
episodes.overview: While investigating the suicide of a retired Navy officer who left a rare, valuable - and possibly stolen - coin to the National Museum of the Navy, the team imagines themselves in his life story in order to piece together how the coin ended up in his possession.

guest_stars.character: Retired Navy Master Chief Arturo 'Art' Amador
guest_stars.name: Joe Renteria

episodes.name: In a Nutshell
episodes.overview: As the NCIS team investigates the death of a Navy officer murdered the same way as his parents a decade ago, they stumble across a storage container filled with dollhouses that display recreations of murder scenes. The team agrees to clean out their living spaces, but some have a harder time saying goodbye to their possessions than others.

episodes.name: Schooled
episodes.overview: The team searches for answers when the body of a well-regarded Navy technician in the Reserves is found floating in a lake where a popular community event is being held. Sloane is caught off-guard when her daughter makes an unexpected request.

episodes.name: Blarney
episodes.overview: When Kasie and Jimmy are held hostage in a diner after a jewelry store robbery goes awry, they attempt to keep the other customers safe from the thieves.

episodes.name: The Arizona
episodes.overview: The team tries to verify the identity of Joe Smith, who claims he served on the U.S.S. Arizona during the attack on Pearl Harbor, and wants to be buried there upon his death.

episodes.name: Sturgeon Season
episodes.overview: Gibbs and Fornell attempt to track down the leader of a drug ring who supplied drugs to Fornell's daughter. Also, the team deals with the case of a missing cadaver from the NCIS autopsy room.

guest_stars.character: Karl Chunk / Homeless Guy / Arda Dogan
guest_stars.name: Brian Stepanek

episodes.name: Everything Starts Somewhere
episodes.overview: Flashbacks reveal the murder case that first introduced young Gibbs to NCIS and his introduction to young, new-to-America Ducky.

episodes.name: Blood And Treasure
episodes.overview: The discovery of two dead bodies  leads the NCIS team into the wild world of modern-day treasure hunting. Also, Gibbs and Fornell get deeper into their search for the opioid kingpin.

episodes.name: Sunburn
episodes.overview: McGee and his wife Delilah's (Margo Harshman) Bahamian vacation turns into a high-stakes mission when a case NCIS is tracking of a dead escape room manager has ties to the island. Also, Gibbs fears the worst when his search for Fornell leads to blood.

episodes.name: Head of the Snake
episodes.overview: Gibbs and Fornell's crusade to find the head of the drug ring responsible for Fornell's daughter Emily's overdose comes to a climax. Also, Gibbs and Vance finally let the team in on a case that has dangerous implications.

episodes.name: 1mm
episodes.overview: Following a tip about smuggled weapons, Bishop and Torres engage in a shootout in a former sheriff's residence that's now a historical site, only to find themselves locked in abandoned jail cells there.

episodes.name: The First Day
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates the murder of a Navy officer who was killed while driving home a recently released inmate. Also, Gibbs helps Palmer deal with a personal trauma.

episodes.name: True Believer
episodes.overview: When Sloane’s name is discovered in Afghanistan at the site of an abandoned bus with a dead driver, Gibbs accompanies her on a trip to find a group of girls who were kidnapped from the bus. McGee, Bishop and Torres track down a hacker who emailed compromising information to the Taliban.

episodes.name: Winter Chill
episodes.overview: NCIS dives into the competitive world of food trucks after finding a man frozen to death in the back of one.

episodes.name: Watchdog
episodes.overview: NCIS uncovers a secret dogfighting ring, which leads to an unexpected move by one of the team members.

episodes.name: Gut Punch
episodes.overview: Vance assigns McGee, Torres, and Bishop to Covid compliance duty at a foreign affairs summit, where they discover a link to another NCIS team's murder case.

guest_stars.character: U.S. Secretary of Defense Moses McClaine
guest_stars.name: William Allen Young

episodes.name: Sangre
episodes.overview: Evidence from the stabbing of a Marine Sergeant leads Torres to meet his father who left when he was a child.

episodes.name: Misconduct
episodes.overview: The team investigates a cyclist killed in a hit and run. Gibbs prepares to testify against a financial advisor who stole millions from his Navy clients.

episodes.name: Unseen Improvements
episodes.overview: NCIS tracks a stolen laptop to the uncle of a young boy, Phineas, Gibbs’ former neighbor.

episodes.name: Blown Away
episodes.overview: When members of an NCIS Regional Enforcement Action Capabilities Training Team (REACT) are killed during an explosion, NCIS Special Agent Jessica Knight (Katrina Law), the lone surviving member, helps crack the case using high tech body armor.

guest_stars.character: NCIS REACT Supervisory Special Agent Tom Dalton
guest_stars.name: Chris Browning

guest_stars.name: Edward Gelhaus

guest_stars.name: Tim Fox

guest_stars.name: Emmie Nagata

episodes.name: Rule 91
episodes.overview: While pursuing a dangerous arms dealer, the team is shocked when Bishop is implicated in an old NSA leak while Gibbs and Marcie realize the killer they've been tracking may be onto them.

episodes.name: Blood in the Water
episodes.overview: As the NCIS team searches for Gibbs after wreckage from his boat is discovered, they find out he was tracking a serial killer with journalist Marcie Warren, who wrote an exposé on him.

episodes.name: Nearly Departed
episodes.overview: While trying to find the serial killer Gibbs was after, the NCIS team discovers another person has been tracking the case as well.

episodes.name: Road to Nowhere
episodes.overview: Gibbs and Parker go on a road trip to find one of the serial killer's victims. Also, Agent Knight goes undercover at a large manufacturing company with ties to the murders.

episodes.name: Great Wide Open
episodes.overview: Gibbs and McGee head to Alaska while the team works at home to uncover the conspiracy behind the serial killer.

episodes.name: Face the Strange
episodes.overview: The NCIS team investigates the death of a Navy officer whose body suddenly explodes before Jimmy can examine it.

episodes.name: False Start
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates the death of a beloved Navy commander who trained some of the top athletes in the country.

episodes.name: Docked
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates the death of a man on a cruise ship whose body is discovered in the ship's sauna by none other than McGee's mother-in-law, Judy.

episodes.name: Peacekeeper
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates the case of a Navy reservist whose body is found in a beat-up car at the end of a gun range. Kasie weighs the pros and cons of buying a gun.

episodes.name: Collective Memory
episodes.overview: When a hotshot financial advisor is found shot at a naval station, NCIS investigates the case by interviewing the victim’s three-dimensional hologram of herself, which she created before her death.

episodes.name: Pledge of Allegiance
episodes.overview: NCIS is called in when Navy Chief Warrant Officer Rafi Nazar is suspected of trying to sell stolen classified Navy software used to pilot combat drones.

episodes.name: All Hands
episodes.overview: After a civilian research vessel in the North Atlantic picks up a small boat of wounded Navy officers, NCIS arrives on the ship and is forced to hide after discovering terrorists on board. Also, Agent Knight takes a paper doll with her on the mission to capture photos for her niece’s grade school class.

episodes.name: Fight or Flight
episodes.overview: When the body of a Navy lieutenant is discovered missing an eye, the NCIS investigation leads to the world of cage fighting.

episodes.name: The Helpers
episodes.overview: While investigating the death of an intruder at Quantico, Jimmy and Kasie are exposed to a deadly biotoxin; the NCIS team calls on Dr. Carol Wilson for help as they race to find the antidote; Torres tries to distract Jimmy's daughter.

episodes.name: First Steps
episodes.overview: As NCIS investigates the cause of death of a reservist Navy SEAL surgeon, they're forced to bring Vance's daughter to help with a highly dangerous mission.

episodes.name: Thick As Thieves
episodes.overview: Parker’s delinquent past resurfaces when NCIS is called to Philadelphia to investigate the death of a Navy petty officer.

episodes.name: The Wake
episodes.overview: A gruesome mishap at a Navy petty officer’s gender-reveal party leads NCIS to the case of a missing teacher that was popularized on a true crime podcast.

episodes.name: Starting Over (I)
episodes.overview:
NCIS investigates the apparent suicide of a retired Navy officer who was in Palmer and Knight's grief group; Torres gets a call from NCIS Special Agent Jane Tennant to come to Hawai'i.

The crossover continues on NCIS: Hawai'i S01E18 T'N'T (II).

episodes.name: Last Dance
episodes.overview: When an infamous arms dealer, Reymundo Diaz, is released from prison and bodies start piling up, Torres is forced to face the repercussions of his actions during an undercover operation he worked on years ago.

episodes.name: The Brat Pack
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates a ring of clever teenage partygoers when a string of break-ins takes place at Marine Base Quantico. While working the case, Special Agent McGee forms a bond with one of the teens, Teagan Fields.

episodes.name: All or Nothing
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates the unexpected death of a Navy reservist who was an investigative journalist. Also, Knight and Jimmy’s budding romance is put on hold when a vital organ transfer goes fatally wrong.

episodes.name: Birds of a Feather
episodes.overview: When Agent Parker is framed for murder, the team puts their jobs and lives on the line to buy time and uncover the truth.

episodes.name: A Family Matter (I)
episodes.overview:
Special Agent Alden Parker is still on the run with his ex-wife Vivian, so the team investigates who from his past might have a personal vendetta against him in hopes of clearing Parker's name.

The crossover continues on NCIS: Hawai'i S02E01 Prisoners' Dilemma (II).

episodes.name: Daddy Issues
episodes.overview: McGee’s personal life and professional life intersect when a dad from his children’s school is linked to a break-in at a government storage bunker.

episodes.name: Unearth
episodes.overview: When a dead body is found at an ancient burial site that is thought to be cursed, the team tries to determine the motive and the symbolism behind the crime. Also, as Torres continues therapy with Dr. Grace, he discovers that their lives are in danger.

episodes.name: Leave No Trace
episodes.overview: Agent Knight's past resurfaces when her ex-boyfriend, a National Parks Service agent, teams up with NCIS to investigate a campsite murder.

episodes.name: Guardian
episodes.overview: Agent Parker steps up to protect Director Vance after a terrifying home invasion. Also, the team detects advancements in Jessica and Jimmy’s blossoming romance.

episodes.name: The Good Fighter
episodes.overview: When an NCIS agent turns up dead and Kasie goes unaccounted for, the team must work quickly to find the killer.

episodes.name: Love Lost
episodes.overview: NCIS must investigate the Secretary of the Navy when her husband claims she tried to murder him.

guest_stars.character: Secretary of the Navy Tara Flynn
guest_stars.name: Carolyn Hennesy

episodes.name: Turkey Trot
episodes.overview: After an unknown shooter causes chaos at an annual Thanksgiving 5K, time is of the essence for the NCIS team to find the culprit. Also, Kasie joins Knight for Thanksgiving lunch at Knight’s sister’s house.

episodes.name: Higher Education
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates the death of a college student who was killed while running across the street and had connections to McGee’s wife, Delilah.

episodes.name: Too Many Cooks (I)
episodes.overview:
NCIS agents from Washington, D.C., Los Angeles and Hawai’i, all in D.C. to attend the retirement party of a beloved Federal Law Enforcement Training Center (FLETC) professor, find themselves jointly investigating his shocking suicide.

The crossover continues on NCIS: Hawai'i S02E10 Deep Fake (II) and NCIS: Los Angeles S14E10 A Long Time Coming (III).

episodes.name: Bridges
episodes.overview: Parker discovers he's a victim of identity theft while investigating the unusual murder of a Navy ensign; Knight and Jimmy face hurdles in their relationship as their connection heightens.

episodes.name: Big Rig
episodes.overview: When an old pal of Torres’ comes to him, disheveled and bloodied for guidance amidst an undercover FBI operation and then disappears, NCIS helps track him down. Also, McGee prepares to be a contestant on a popular game show

episodes.name: Evil Eye
episodes.overview: In preparation for a role, a world-renowned actress shadows the NCIS team as they investigate a decapitation case.

episodes.name: Old Wounds
episodes.overview: Parker grapples with his emotions when a conman from his past turns up as a prime suspect in the murder of a navy officer transporting millions of dollars’ worth of opioids.

episodes.name: Unusual Suspects
episodes.overview: NCIS investigates the death of a ride-share driver who was found after a car accident. Also, Parker’s dad, who is temporarily living with him, assists the team in their investigation.

episodes.name: Butterfly Effect
episodes.overview: The NCIS team jumps into motion to investigate who is responsible for a potential bioterror attack at a strip mall parking garage; Knight's father deals with a health scare while in Japan.

episodes.name: Stranger in a Strange Land
episodes.overview: NCIS works to solve the murder of a Marine private who appears to have been killed for helping an Afghan refugee. Also, Jimmy navigates the pressure of parenting his teenage daughter, who is eager to go out on an unchaperoned group date.

episodes.name: Head Games
episodes.overview: The NCIS team digs deep to investigate a Navy lieutenant who’s accused of trying to murder her husband but has no memory of the attack. Also, Kasie navigates a potential medical scare.

episodes.name: In the Spotlight
episodes.overview: Agent Knight goes viral for saving a mother and child from a potentially fatal car accident.

episodes.name: Second Opinion
episodes.overview: NCIS works to solve the murder of a senator’s daughter who has a rebellious reputation and large online following. Also, Jimmy gets competitive with an old college rival.

episodes.name: Kompromat
episodes.overview: When a suspicious murder occurs in the classified section of the National Archive, NCIS must investigate a string of Russian spy encounters that may be linked to the crime. Also, Jimmy accidentally makes a confession that could change the course of his relationship with Knight.

episodes.name: Black Sky
episodes.overview: Agent Torres finds himself in prison as the team tries to stop an impending terror attack on U.S. soil.

episodes.name: Algún Día
episodes.overview: The NCIS team must help Torres when he puts his future at stake by confronting the man who tormented his family when he was a child.

episodes.name: The Stories We Leave Behind
episodes.overview: As NCIS mourns the loss of Ducky, the agents find comfort in working on one of his unfinished cases involving a woman whose father was dishonorably discharged from the Marines.

episodes.name: Lifeline
episodes.overview: When the NCIS team engages in Walk-a-Mile day to gain a new perspectives on different departments, things take a turn when Kasie receives a distress call from a mysterious man.

episodes.name: Left Unsaid
episodes.overview: The NCIS team is in a race against time to find a missing officer who disappeared during his wedding proposal.

episodes.name: The Plan
episodes.overview: With the help of Knight's dad, NCIS works to unravel the mystery of a recently used service weapon belonging to a missing agent. Also, McGee is in a tailspin when DNA results reveal a close relative he was unaware of.

guest_stars.character: Special Agent in Charge Feng Zhao
guest_stars.name: Russell Wong

episodes.name: Strange Invaders
episodes.overview: After discovering a navy pilot's body riddled with unusual wounds, NCIS' investigation draws the team into the rabbit hole of UFO conspiracy theories.

episodes.name: A Thousand Yards
episodes.overview: NCIS comes under attack by a mysterious enemy from the past. Also, Vance tries to mend fences with his estranged son by explaining why, despite the ongoing dangers of his job, he still chooses to stay at NCIS.

episodes.name: Heartless
episodes.overview: The NCIS team looks for a motive behind the kidnapping and death of a famous heart surgeon.

episodes.name: Prime Cut
episodes.overview: After discovering the remains of a Marine captain, the NCIS team travels to Texas to interrogate the suspected killer.

episodes.name: Reef Madness
episodes.overview: Parker and Knight discover three bodies on an old Navy ship that's about to be sunk and turned into an artificial reef, when they're suddenly locked inside by a mysterious figure. Also, Vance offers Knight a unique opportunity.

episodes.name: Empty Nest
episodes.overview: NCIS searches for a missing undercover agent in the midst of an active hostage situation.

episodes.name: Foreign Bodies
episodes.overview: As Vance prepares to host diplomatic talks with Venezuela, the team is called in to investigate the dead body of one of his inside men.

episodes.name: The Trouble with Hal
episodes.overview: NCIS is called in to investigate when a lieutenant returns home on the eve of Halloween to find a surprise party being thrown for someone else at his place.

episodes.name: Sticks & Stones
episodes.overview: After receiving intelligence on deadly threats to multiple locations that could lead to a catastrophic war, NCIS is called in to try to neutralize the danger.

episodes.name: In from the Cold
episodes.overview: NCIS works with the CIA to discover what secrets are being kept by Capt. Butler, an aging former spy.
